---
---
<section class="diff-sec" id="porque">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="sec-head fade">
      <p class="sec-eyebrow">Por qué Gisus</p>
      <h2 class="display sec-title">Diseñado para el mundo real.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="diff-grid">
      <!-- Card 1: real-time radar (accent) -->
      <div class="diff-card accent fade">
        <div class="diff-visual">
          <div class="dv-radar">
            <div class="dv-disk">
              <div class="dv-ring dv-r1"></div><div class="dv-ring dv-r2"></div><div class="dv-ring dv-r3"></div>
              <div class="dv-glow"></div><div class="dv-sweep"></div><div class="dv-you"></div>
              <div class="dv-dot" style="top:28%;left:64%;width:28px;height:28px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FF2D78,#FF6B9D)">A</div>
              <div class="dv-dot" style="top:66%;left:32%;width:24px;height:24px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6B4FFF,#9B7FFF)">L</div>
              <div class="dv-dot" style="top:72%;left:70%;width:22px;height:22px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#2DD4BF,#06B6D4)">S</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="diff-h">Tiempo real, sin GPS</h3>
        <p class="diff-p">Proximidad real sin acceder a tu ubicación ni vaciar tu batería. Más inmediato y preciso que cualquier app basada en mapa.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: privacy -->
      <div class="diff-card fade" style="transition-delay:.08s">
        <div class="diff-visual">
          <div class="dv-ids">
            <div class="dv-id">ID · 9F2A7C</div>
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" style="opacity:.5"><path d="M12 4v10m0 0l-4-4m4 4l4-4" stroke="#FF2D78" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            <div class="dv-id fade-id">ID · D6B1E0</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="diff-h">Privacidad por diseño</h3>
        <p class="diff-p">Tu identificador rota automáticamente cada pocos minutos. Nadie puede rastrearte: solo existes en el radar de quien está cerca contigo.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: only present people -->
      <div class="diff-card fade" style="transition-delay:.16s">
        <div class="diff-visual">
          <div class="dv-cluster">
            <div class="dv-pin" style="top:0;left:38%"><div class="av" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FF2D78,#FF6B9D)">A</div><div class="d">8m</div></div>
            <div class="dv-pin" style="top:90px;left:4%"><div class="av" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6B4FFF,#9B7FFF)">L</div><div class="d">14m</div></div>
            <div class="dv-pin" style="top:110px;left:62%"><div class="av" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FF8C42,#FFC542)">S</div><div class="d">22m</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="diff-h">Solo personas presentes</h3>
        <p class="diff-p">Nada de perfiles a 40 km. Si aparece en tu radar, está en el mismo café, evento o parque que tú. En este momento preciso.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: instant chat -->
      <div class="diff-card fade" style="transition-delay:.24s">
        <div class="diff-visual">
          <div class="dv-chat">
            <div class="dv-msg in">¿También estás en la librería? 😊</div>
            <div class="dv-msg out">¡Sí! En la sección de filosofía</div>
            <div class="dv-msg in">Voy para allá 📚</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h3 class="diff-h">Chat que nace del momento</h3>
        <p class="diff-p">El match abre un chat directo. La conversación fluye mientras siguen compartiendo el mismo espacio. Justo aquí, justo ahora.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .diff-sec { padding: 120px 0; }
  .sec-head { max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 70px; }
  .sec-eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--pink); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .sec-title { font-size: clamp(34px, 4.4vw, 60px); }
  .diff-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 22px; margin-top: 56px; }
  .diff-card { background: var(--pink-soft); border-radius: 34px; padding: 44px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; min-height: 440px; transition: transform .3s; }
  .diff-card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); }
  .diff-card.accent { background: var(--grad); color: #fff; }
  .diff-visual { flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 30px; min-height: 200px; }
  .diff-h { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 800; font-size: 30px; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: -0.015em; }
  .diff-p { font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.55; color: var(--ink-soft); text-wrap: pretty; max-width: 440px; }
  .diff-card.accent .diff-p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.9); }

  .dv-radar { position: relative; width: 200px; height: 200px; }
  .dv-disk { width:100%; height:100%; border-radius:50%; background: rgba(255,255,255,.5); border:1.5px solid rgba(255,45,120,.25); overflow:hidden; position:relative; }
  .dv-ring { position:absolute; border-radius:50%; border:1px solid rgba(255,45,120,.3); top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%); }
  .dv-r1{width:36%;height:36%;} .dv-r2{width:68%;height:68%;} .dv-r3{width:100%;height:100%;}
  .dv-sweep { position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; width:50%; height:2px; transform-origin:left center; background:linear-gradient(to right,transparent,#FF2D78); animation: spin 4s linear infinite; }
  .dv-glow { position:absolute; inset:0; border-radius:50%; background: conic-gradient(from 0deg, transparent 60%, rgba(255,45,120,.14) 100%); animation: spin 4s linear infinite; }
  .dv-you { position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%); width:14px; height:14px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--grad); box-shadow:0 0 0 5px rgba(255,45,120,.16); z-index:5; }
  .dv-dot { position:absolute; transform:translate(-50%,-50%); border-radius:50%; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-family:var(--font-display); font-weight:800; font-size:11px; color:#fff; border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.7); }

  .dv-ids { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; align-items: center; }
  .dv-id { font-family: 'SF Mono', ui-monospace, monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; background: rgba(255,255,255,.25); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.4); padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 100px; letter-spacing: .04em; }
  .dv-id.fade-id { opacity: .4; }

  .dv-cluster { position: relative; width: 220px; height: 180px; }
  .dv-pin { position: absolute; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 4px; }
  .dv-pin .av { width: 46px; height: 46px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 800; font-size: 16px; color: #fff; border: 3px solid var(--pink-soft); }
  .dv-pin .d { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--pink); background: #fff; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 100px; }

  .dv-chat { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; width: 240px; }
  .dv-msg { font-size: 14px; padding: 11px 15px; border-radius: 16px; max-width: 82%; line-height: 1.4; }
  .dv-msg.in { background: rgba(255,255,255,.7); color: var(--ink); align-self: flex-start; border-radius: 16px 16px 16px 4px; }
  .dv-msg.out { background: var(--grad); color: #fff; align-self: flex-end; border-radius: 16px 16px 4px 16px; }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .diff-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .diff-card { min-height: 0; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .diff-card { padding: 34px 28px; }
  }
</style>
